Planet korr, definys gans [[Unyans Steroniethek Keswlasek]], yw korf nevek ow resa a-dro an howl<ref name="finalresolution">[http://www.iau.org/static/resolutions/Resolution_GA26-5-6.pdf Definition of a Planet in the Solar System: Resolutions 5 and 6 (IAU 2006 General Assembly)]</ref> neb yw gronnedhek lowr dhos ha bos pelyek awos gravedh y honan mes na re klerhas y ranndir a planetesimalys, ha nyns yw loor.<ref name="iau">[http://www.iau.org/iau0603.414.0.html IAU 2006 General Assembly: Result of the IAU Resolution votes]</ref><ref>[http://solarsystem.nasa.gov/planets/profile.cfm?Object=Dwarf (Dwarf Planets, NASA)]</ref> Yma edhomm dhodho gronnedh lowr dhe fedha y nerth gwaskek ha drehedhes komposter hydrostatyk. 

An hanow "planet korr" a veu adoptys yn 2006 yn unn glassans korfow ow resea a-dro an howl yn teyr rann. Yth esa moghheans yn diskudhansow taklennow treus-Nevyon neb a gesstrivyas erbynn [[Plouton_(planet_korr)|Plouton]] yn braster, hag yn gortiwedh an diskudhans Eris,<ref name="mass">[http://www.sciencemag.org/content/316/5831/1585 The Mass of Dwarf Planet Eris (Brown et al. 2007, Science, 2007Sci...316.1585B)]</ref> taklenn gans moy a ronnedh es [[Plouton_(planet_korr)|Pluton]]. An klassans a lever bos korfow gronnedhek lowr dhe glerhe ranndir aga resekva gelwys "planetys", hag an re nag yw gronnedhek lowr dhe dhos ha bos pelyek awos gravedh y honan bos gelwys "korfow byghan system howlek". Yntredha, yma planetys korr. An styryans adoptys yn sodhogel gans an [[Unyans Steroniethek Keswlasek|USK]] re veu lawa hag arvreusys, ha disputys gans godhonydhyon kepar hag Alan Stern.<ref name="Stern">[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/5283956.stm Pluto vote 'hijacked' in revolt]</ref><ref name="Stern2009">[http://www.earthsky.org/interviewpost/space/alan-stern-%E2%80%98a-chihuahua-is-still-a-dog-and-pluto-is-still-a-planet Alan Stern: ‘A Chihuahua is still a dog, and Pluto is still a planet']</ref>

An [[Unyans Steroniethek Keswlasek|USK]] a aswonn pymp planetys korr y'n termyn ma: [[Ceres (planet còr)|Ceres]], [[Pluton (planet)|Pluton]], [[Haumea]], [[Makemake]] ha [[Eris]].<ref name="WGPSN">[http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/append7.html#DwarfPlanets Dwarf Planets and their Systems (Working Group for Planetary System Nomenclature (WGPSN))]</ref> Dew hepken, [[Ceres]] ha [[Pluton]] re veu mires yn ta lowr dhe brevi aga bos pelyek lowr ha kewera an styryans. Steronydhyon a grys [[Eris]] yw pelyek lowr drefenn y vos brassa y ronnedh es [[Pluton (planet)|Pluton]]. Diwettha, an [[Unyans Steroniethek Keswlasek|USK]] a erviras res yw taklennow treus-Nevyon heb hanow gans myns pur golowa es +1 (ha dredho braster kalkys gans awrgym moy ages 838 km)<ref name="bruton">[http://www.physics.sfasu.edu/astro/asteroids/sizemagnitude.html Conversion of Absolute Magnitude to Diameter for Minor Planets (Department of Physics & Astronomy (Stephen F. Austin State University), Dan Bruton)]</ref> bos henwys yn-dann desev planetys korr yns.

Gogrysys yw moy ages dew ugens taklennow aswonnys erell yn system howlek yw planetys korr, ha bys dew kans planetys korr yn ranndir gelwys [[grogys Kuiper]]. <ref name="Brown">[http://web.gps.caltech.edu/~mbrown/dwarfplanets/ The Dwarf Planets (Michael E. Brown)]</ref>

Ny wrug klassans korfow haval orth planetys korr yn systemow planettys erell bos prederys. <ref name="Draft Resolution 5">[http://www.iau.org/public_press/news/release/iau0601/ The IAU draft definition of "planet" and "plutons"]</ref>

